carDescription: The Mustang roars with raw power, a legendary American muscle car. Sleek, aerodynamic design meets brute force, equipped with a high-performance engine that delivers thrilling acceleration and a distinctive exhaust note. Its heritage commands attention on the road, making it an icon of speed and style.

The Ford F-150, a rugged and versatile full-size pickup truck. Combining robust construction with advanced technology, it's a workhorse and a comfortable ride. Boasting impressive towing and hauling capabilities, it's the epitome of reliability.
